Class AbsPrimitive

java.lang.Object
jade.content.abs.AbsPrimitive
All Implemented Interfaces:
AbsObject, AbsTerm, Term, Serializable
public class AbsPrimitive extends Object implements AbsTerm
An abstract descriptor that can hold a primitive expression.
